channel.description:
hi i was wondering how i put my server on hamachi server? ill tell you the lists i got downloaded so far
-pimpscape server source -hamachi -java 6u2 -no-ip but i dont think i need -WinRAR -modzilla -and i got compile.bat. and runserver.bat
what else i need to do to put my hamachi server on and make people play i dont know how to make people play ive registered my hamachi server already.
first like 5 people to help will be admins on my hamachi.
